途採用</strong>\n              <small class=\"font-en color-gre\">Entry For Career Recruitment</small>\n            </h3>\n            <i><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/common/mail.png\" height=\"48\" width=\"64\" alt=\"中途応募\"></i>\n          </a>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </nav>\n    <hr>\n    <h1 class=\"header--logo\">\n      <a href=\"/recruitment/\">\n        <small>株式会社市川工務店 リクルートサイト</small>\n        <img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/common/head_logo.png\" alt=\"市川工務店の仕事｜岐阜県の総合建設企業で働くなら｜㈱市川工務店\" width=\"140\" height=\"44\">\n      </a>\n    </h1>\n    <hr>\n    <div class=\"entry_btn sp-none\">\n      <a href=\"#entry\" class=\"font-jp-min smooth\"><span class=\"font-en\">Entry</span>応募する</a>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  \n    <!-- start page_ttl -->\n    <div class=\"page_ttl\"  id=\"page_ttl\">\n      <h2 class=\"inner\">\n                <span class=\"page_ttl-jp\">市川工務店の仕事</span>\n                <span class=\"page_ttl-en\">business</span>\n      </h2>\n    </div>\n    <!-- end page_ttl -->\n\n  \r\n<main class=\"business\" id=\"business\">\r\n  \r\n  <section class=\"business_section bg-pt1 section_pdg page_intro flex-a-ctr flex\" id=\"public_section\">\r\n    <div class=\"inner inner-lg\">\r\n      <h2 class=\"section_ttl mgn-btm24\">\r\n        <strong>土木工事・舗装工事</strong>\r\n        <small class=\"color-bro\">Civil Enginnerring</small>\r\n      </h2>\r\n      <p class=\"txt-ctr txt-sp-lft mgn-btm40\">高速道路・国道・県道といった道路工事と河川工事、トンネル工事、ダム工事などの土木工事・道路の舗装工事など、<br class=\"sp-none\">地域になくてはならない社会インフラを支える工事が中心。<br class=\"sp-none\">これからも人々が安心して暮らせる街をつくりあげる使命があります。</p>\r\n      <ul class=\"flex flex-col3 flex-sp-col2 mgn-btm32\">\r\n        <li>\r\n          <div class=\"img mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/business/public_img1.jpg\" alt=\"ささゆりトンネル\"></div>\r\n          <p class=\"txt-sm\">ささゆりトンネル</p>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li>\r\n          <div class=\"img mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/business/public_img2.jpg\" alt=\"鵜飼い大橋\"></div>\r\n          <p class=\"txt-sm\">鵜飼い大橋</p>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li>\r\n          <div class=\"img mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/business/public_img3.jpg\" alt=\"国道248号道路舗装\"></div>\r\n          <p class=\"txt-sm\">国道248号道路舗装</p>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li>\r\n          <div class=\"img mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/business/public_img4.jpg\" alt=\"小島山トンネル\"></div>\r\n          <p class=\"txt-sm\">小島山トンネル</p>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li>\r\n          <div class=\"img mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/business/public_img5.jpg\" alt=\"丹生川ダム\"></div>\r\n          <p class=\"txt-sm\">丹生川ダム</p>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li>\r\n          <div class=\"img mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/business/public_img6.jpg\" alt=\"長良川東島地区護岸工事\"></div>\r\n          <p class=\"txt-sm\">長良川 東島地区護岸工事</p>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li>\r\n          <div class=\"img mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/business/public_img7.jpg\" alt=\"東海環状自動車道\"></div>\r\n          <p class=\"txt-sm\">東海環状自動車道</p>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li>\r\n          <div class=\"img mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/business/public_img8.jpg\" alt=\"名神高速道路 安八スマートインターチェンジ\"></div>\r\n          <p class=\"txt-sm\">名神高速道路 安八スマートインターチェンジ</p>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li class=\"sp-none\">\r\n          <div class=\"img mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/business/public_img9.jpg\" alt=\"木曽川 小網樋管\"></div>\r\n          <p class=\"txt-sm\">木曽川 小網樋管</p>\r\n        </li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n      <p class=\"txt-ctr\"><a href=\"https://www.ic-group.co.jp/projects/ewi.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"btn new_tab\">土木の事例をもっと見る</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </section>\r\n  <section class=\"business_section section_pdg flex flex-a-ctr flex-reverse\" id=\"architecture_section\">\r\n    <div class=\"inner inner-lg\">\r\n      <h2 class=\"section_ttl mgn-btm24\">\r\n        <strong>建築工事</strong>\r\n        <small class=\"color-gre\">Architecture</small>\r\n      </h2>\r\n      <p class=\"txt-ctr txt-sp-lft mgn-btm40\">学校・警察署・消防署などの公共施設のほか、地元企業の工場、倉庫、事務所・店舗などの建築工事で地域のみなさんの暮らしを支える事業。<br class=\"sp-none\">その他にも企業の事務所、工場のほか住宅のリフォーム工事にも対応するため、キャリアやスキルに合わせて業務が割り振られます。<br class=\"sp-none\">人々の暮らしを豊かにする仕事です。</p>\r\n      <ul class=\"flex flex-col3 flex-sp-col2 mgn-btm32\">\r\n        <li>\r\n          <div class=\"img mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/business/architecture_img1.jpg\" alt=\"ぎふメディアコスモス立体駐車場\"></div>\r\n          <p class=\"txt-sm\">ぎふメディアコスモス立体駐車場</p>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li>\r\n          <div class=\"img mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/business/architecture_img2.jpg\" alt=\"株式会社ハートランス本社及び流通センター\"></div>\r\n          <p class=\"txt-sm\">株式会社ハートランス本社及び流通センター</p>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li>\r\n          <div class=\"img mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/business/architecture_img3.jpg\" alt=\"岐阜市長良川防災・健康ステーション\"></div>\r\n          <p class=\"txt-sm\">岐阜市長良川防災・健康ステーション</p>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li class=\"sp-none\">\r\n          <div class=\"img mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/business/architecture_img4.jpg\" alt=\"岐阜清流高等特別支援学校\"></div>\r\n          <p class=\"txt-sm\">岐阜清流高等特別支援学校</p>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li>\r\n          <div class=\"img mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/business/architecture_img5.jpg\" alt=\"岐阜南警察署\"></div>\r\n          <p class=